MVC:-
Model----->UI data
view------>response(output)
controller------->only one controller---->Servlet,Filter


Spring MVC :-

	Spring provided Controller   ---------> servlet --------->DispatcherServlet
	DD---->Deployment Descriptor--->web.xml
	
	
	<servlet>
		<servlet-name>Spring</servlet-name>
	</servlet>
	
Front controller
	Which is the Configuration?---><filename-servlet>.xml
	ex:<Spring-servlet>.xml
	
	<component scan base-package com.controller>
	<component scan base-package com.model>
	<component scan base-package com.dao>
	<component scan base-package com.appexception>

class MyController
{
	public String function()
	{
		//logic
		return "Hello";//view page
	}
}

InternalViewResolver--->
		prefix	before	"folder"	view page------>hello.jsp
		postfix	after	.jsp
	
